description: Stylish Bi-Level Condo – Just 3 Blocks from the Beach! This fully renovated home in 2017, once the historic Quencher Tavern, blends modern comfort with a prime South Boston location between East Broadway and Carson Beach. The two-level layout offers two bedrooms and two bathrooms with new plumbing, electrical, and HVAC systems. Enjoy a designer kitchen with shaker cabinets, quartz counters, and stainless appliances. Hardwood floors, central A/C, and recessed lighting complete the polished look. The flexible lower-level bedroom easily functions as an office, guest room, or family space. Step outside to your exclusive stone patio—ideal for relaxing or entertaining. With the beach just moments away, this turn-key condo delivers unbeatable convenience and charm.
